  "scenes": [
    {
      "scene_index": 1,
      "label": "第一场",
      "characters_present": [
        "陆贾"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套引陆贾同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，陆贾。奉了大王之命，捉拿蒯彻。\n来，打道前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 2,
          "白": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "乞丐乙",
        "乞丐甲",
        "蒯彻",
        "陆贾"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蒯彻上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "实指望忠心来报国，\n又谁知无故起风波。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，蒯……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蒯彻两下观望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，蒯彻，字文通；汉室为臣。只因韩元帅登坛拜将，官封三齐王之职，圣上\n听信谗言，道他谋反，就将他斩首在未央宫。可恨那萧何老儿，又在万岁台前\n奏道，说那韩元帅造反是我蒯彻主谋，要拿我问罪。是我假装疯颠，在此躲避。\n苍天吓，天。想当初楚汉争锋之时，那项羽兵临咸阳城下，无人对敌，那时\n我主言道，有人退却楚兵，加官受赏。又道是：“如若霸王坏，三齐王即拜；\n如若霸王在，三齐王无人戴。”不想那韩元帅，将项羽围困在九里山前，十面\n埋伏，立逼霸王乌江命丧；即封韩元帅为三齐王。四方平定，江山一统，反把\n个盖世英雄斩首在未央宫中。思想起来，好不伤感人也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "提起了韩元帅珠泪双落，\n好叫我蒯文通咬碎牙窝。\n韩元帅领雄兵大起干戈。\n立逼那楚霸王命见阎罗。\n怎想到未央宫把他的头割。\n无奈何我只得假装疯魔。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二乞丐同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "数板",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吃得饱，睡得着，世人都没有叫化高。要得多，吃个饱；讨得少，将就了。叫\n化回来睡上一觉，一睡睡的日头大高。终日浪荡乐逍遥，看起来真比做官高。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计：你看咱们要饭，真比做官还好的多啦！一身无挂碍，讨的多来，多吃一\n口；讨的少来，少吃一口。心里什么事也不管，比做官强似百倍。你看他们做\n官的，说是好起来，就是轰轰烈烈；说一个不好，就要杀头问罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闲话少说，今天没有事，咱们去看看那一个疯子，还在那里不在？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，咱们去逗逗他去。嘿！他还在这儿呐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲、乞丐乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喂，疯子！你在这里做什么呐呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蒯彻扯住乞丐乙。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "却原来是我的儿……"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哟，你敢情是他的儿子吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你别开玩笑啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蒯彻扯住乞丐甲。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是他的哥哥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你也是他的儿子。咱们两个人倒成了弟兄啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒯彻 （三笑） 哈哈，吓哈，吓哈哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲、乞丐乙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他笑起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "到如今我与你同欢乐，"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你为什么事，这个样儿的乐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你听了："
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我定要入洞房匹配姣娥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他原来是要娶媳妇吓！我问问你：你的丈人是谁呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听呐："
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我丈人可就是丞相萧何，"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他丈人是当朝宰相萧何，你的丈母娘是谁呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我丈母她就是萧何的老婆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这可倒说得好，丈人是萧何，丈母娘自然是萧何的老婆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "她断不能是你的老婆！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你别胡说啦。我再问问你：是谁与你做的媒人呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听了："
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我的媒原来是秦始皇来做，"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，他的媒原来是秦始皇做的。那么你的媳妇是谁呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我的妻她就是月里嫦娥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他说他的妻子就是月里嫦娥。伙计，这嫦娥你可曾见过么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我没有见过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你没有见过，我可是见过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你在哪里见过？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看见过梅兰芳的《嫦娥奔月》。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那是戏！"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那是“戏”。咱们唱的，难道说不是戏么？\n既是娶亲，可有人与你贺喜么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "满朝中文武臣俱来庆贺，"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "满朝文武俱来庆贺，你给他们什么吃呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我与他山珍海错、珍馐美味、还有那熊掌燕窝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你听见没有？他说熊掌燕窝。这熊掌我们是没有吃过；这燕窝我可是吃过的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你在哪里吃过？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看那破庙的房檐底下，小燕搭的窝，把他拿下来，切切吃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好吃么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好吃，太牙碜。\n我问你这送亲的是哪一个呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "送亲人可就是你们两个，"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，咱们两人成了大舅子了。\n我们两个人来送亲，有什么好处没有吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我要请你二人吃大餐，再坐马车。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这可就不对了。想那汉朝的时代，焉有大餐马车呐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有道是：孔子圣之时者也。他当年生在列国之时，所以专讲安邦定国，若要生\n在这共和时代，少不得也要如此。况且逢场作戏，你又何必深究吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（内鸣开道锣。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "乞丐甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看那旁有一伙人来了，咱们快走吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二乞丐同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "耳边厢又听得鸣锣声过，\n倘有人到此来又费唇舌。\n怕的是平地里又起风波。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套引陆贾同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这人果在此地，待我下马唤他一声。\n吓，蒯先生，请出来呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "耳旁边又听得有人唤我，\n向前去看他有何话说。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是陆大人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你装的好疯吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "事到如今，只得如此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今有萧何丞相在万岁驾前奏道：三齐王造反是先生与他主谋，特命下官前来，\n拿你治罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，一同前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！先生此番前去，凶多吉少、生死难料，依下官之见，不如快快逃走了吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大丈夫生在世上，生何足欢，死何足惧！来来来，将刑具戴上！"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我一殿为臣，此时不戴也罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "国家法律，焉有不戴之理，拿过来呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我这里将刑具一一戴过，\n此一番到金殿哪顾死活。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
