    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "众人",
        "侍内臣将冠带与蒯卿换上",
        "内监",
        "刘邦",
        "怒气冲冲金殿上",
        "来在金殿用目望",
        "萧何",
        "蒯彻",
        "这一旁站的是萧何丞相",
        "这一班文共武俱是开国之将",
        "陆贾",
        "陈平"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四太监、王陵、樊哙、萧何、陈平引刘邦同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "有孤王上金殿金钟三响，\n文站东武立西排列两厢。\n官封他三齐王扶保朝堂。\n因此上才将他斩首未央。\n等候了陆贾回细问端详。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陆贾上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "盖世忠良无下场，撩袍端带见君王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣陆贾见驾，吾皇万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你捉拿蒯彻，可曾拿到？"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "现在午门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将他绑上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陆贾",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。\n将蒯彻押上来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四校尉押蒯彻同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "韩元帅本是忠良将，\n汗马功劳无下场。\n文臣武将站立两旁。\n那一旁有陈平为国忠良。\n单单不见了三齐王。\n站立在丹墀下对答刘邦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "来在金殿用目望、这一旁站的是萧何丞相、这一班文共武俱是开国之将、怒气冲冲金殿上、刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胆大蒯彻，见了孤家为何不跪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想我蒯彻，自昔侍奉三齐王韩信，今日不见三齐王，你叫我跪哪个？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那韩信谋反，本是你与他主谋，正要将你治罪，你还敢多言！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了！既然说我替韩信主谋，何不将韩信唤来，我二人一同质对。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这……这韩信已斩首在未央宫中了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那韩信，有十大汗马功劳，忠心保国。也不知是何人，诬他造反，不论青红\n皂白，就将他斩首在未央宫中，今日又说是我蒯彻与他主谋。看将起来，你可\n算是昏王无道也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大胆！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "胆大的蒯文通实实狂妄，\n敢在这金殿上辱骂孤王。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四校尉抬油鼎同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "管叫你一霎时命丧无常。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀哈哈哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你为何发笑？"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我笑那三齐王，领兵之时，曾与霸王连番征战，将他诱在九里山前，大埋伏三\n十六，小埋伏七十二，安排十面，围得铁桶一般，霸王无奈，败在乌江，自刎\n而亡。当时若无韩信，怎能一统天下？今日四方已定，太平安享，你反把他斩\n首未央；又听谗言，将彭越杀死。今日又要害我蒯彻，满朝文武各各伤心。凡\n有人心者无不酸鼻落泪也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "忆昔当年三齐王，\n他与项羽动刀枪。\n立逼霸王自刎乌江。\n反把个能征惯战、足智多谋三齐王斩首在未央。\n俱言道盖世功劳反无下场！是何人保你坐朝堂？\n落一个青史名标在万古扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蒯彻扑向油鼎。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听一言倒叫孤无有话讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将油鼎抬下去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四校尉抬油鼎同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "也是孤做事欠思量。"
        },
        {
          "character": "侍内臣将冠带与蒯卿换上、内监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒯先生，走吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "往哪里去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "内监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到朝房去冠带去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是不去的。我是不做官了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "内监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你来吧。不要拿捏了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（内监扯蒯彻同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "这件事是萧何错奏本章。"
        },
        {
          "character": "萧何",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "望万岁开皇恩不把罪降，\n这也是臣萧何奏本荒唐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈平",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "老丞相不该把本来上，\n险些儿又屈杀一个忠良。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "樊哙 （同西皮摇板） 萧丞相切莫要把本乱上，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怕的是忠良臣俱无下场！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "众卿不必纷纷讲，\n快宣蒯彻上朝堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "内监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒯彻上殿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（蒯彻上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一席话说得他龙心释放，\n我这里端玉带忙见君王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣蒯彻叩谢万岁不斩之恩！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卿家平身！"
        },
        {
          "character": "蒯彻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万万岁！适才为臣言语颠狂，还求万岁恕罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘邦",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤不降罪于你。孤王有意，在咸阳城内，起造祠堂一座，供奉彭越、韩信，春\n秋致祭。就命卿家监工筑造。领旨下殿。光禄寺大排筵宴，与众卿贺功。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
